entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text:
539 NEW CASES

The Department of Health reports 539 new COVID-19 cases in the country, bringing the total number to 15,588. 

The department also announces 92 new recoveries and 17 deaths. https://t.co/tfbuEd4Atj
